{"tid":2493394,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大灣區陷阱｜港人深圳買舖遭強佔 網紅餐飲承租","createTime":"2021-04-18T00:44:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T00:57:40.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e17e588c8f64bdf143d14cc4396d4b83dcbb854e","tid":2493394,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:44:55.000Z","msg":"港人近年擁抱有大灣區，惟北上置業路陷阱重重。有港人「早著先機」，於15年前擲近百萬元於深圳東門購買茂業百貨旗下商舖，獲承諾3年租金回報(返租)。豈料，商場營業僅3個月即拉閘，一直丟空直至去年，業主始發現商場已遭擅自出租予內地網紅餐飲企業「文和友」，惟小業主卻不獲一毛錢也分不到。有專家提醒投資者，當「返租」時效完結，物業往往無法出租，或租金遠低於預期，而舖位分拆出售的「劏場」，最終會變「死場」，令業主蒙受損失。<br />\n<br />\n2006年4月，當時僅43歲的Banson認為東門人流旺盛，認為置業具極大升值潛力，為將來退休作準備，亦相信茂業此大品牌，遂購入旗下名為「港島銀座」一個面積27平方米的舖位，發展商深圳茂業集團承諾提供3年租金回報(反租)，共30萬元，直接由樓價扣減，Banson最終實付約91萬元人民幣。他先付3成首期，尾數再分8年供款。<br />\n<br />\nBanson指，共3層高的商場分間成超過300個舖位，大部分由茂業持有，僅約50舖位售予小業主，茂業承諾，3年返租期滿後，業主可將舖位自行出租。Banson的舖位曾出租予鞋店，惟當上業主僅3個月，他與一眾業主發現，商場店舖逐漸減少，僅地面樓層有商舖營業，一個月後更「熄燈拉閘」停止運作。業主曾向發展商查問，獲回覆「正進行規劃，商場出租率需達七成始重開」，其後一直處於膠著狀態，「想租又租唔出，想賣又無人買」。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210417/PBGT62L3GFDAXKJLZ3NHZ5ZXXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210417%2FPBGT62L3GFDAXKJLZ3NHZ5ZXXU%2F&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=256a9203\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210417%2FPBGT62L3GFDAXKJLZ3NHZ5ZXXU%2F&h=5e91e24e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210417/PBGT62L3GFDAXKJLZ3NHZ5ZXXU/</a>"},{"pid":"f545055625fad6fd0ca0011f2d0768b6596a699b","tid":2493394,"uid":18477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:46:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">港島・銀座(支那深圳)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"157ba3e6503329842a2ec665b4b0680f49ddb9b0","tid":2493394,"uid":41914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:48:38.000Z","msg":"以為真係銀座?"},{"pid":"6494a0fe026da8fa9e02eab16a12b8ebf6a80b54","tid":2493394,"uid":71279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:49:26.000Z","msg":"信政府<br />\n唔怕"},{"pid":"25a62d95322d1d6657f4bbbe3d3441e97563a3e7","tid":2493394,"uid":152476,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:49:55.000Z","msg":"大灣區機遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8721ffd01e4cf93e7d18f217f36a9dca3baf6098","tid":2493394,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:51:27.000Z","msg":"麥包有買？"},{"pid":"7d05a82189f1879a0e91c263f2334d8ad64bbc2d","tid":2493394,"uid":358086,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:52:06.000Z","msg":"去大灣區預咗架啦"},{"pid":"477aa1ca9343e8f514810c70aecd996992a0e523","tid":2493394,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"靠大灣區?食得屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877b7a55de7dc484f2adc1d6077fee8322f8d67e","tid":2493394,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T00:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}